data.description: Spacious, well maintained home with finished basement in East Paulding! Upstairs features large family room with vaulted ceiling and fireplace, open kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and gas stove, view to family room, and separate dining area. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout main level living areas. The oversized master bedroom features a master bathroom with granite countertop, large vanity, and separate tub and shower. On the other side of the house are two big secondary bedrooms with bathroom with tub/shower combo. Downstairs is a larger finished space with a half bath. Perfect for guests, home office, play room, or gym! Tons of space for storage and cars in the garage. Long, level driveway in front on a quiet cul de sac! Deck out the back door with gorgeous flat backyard with shed, playground, and fire pit. Super convenient location close to shopping and groceries! No HOA!
